window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The quest to end all quests.</b></p> <p>Ryan Rosa and the rest of the Broken Bones guild have completed their first deeds and have their empire on the way to legendary status, but the other guilds and certain high-ranking members of the game's ownership are doing everything they can to prevent the team from reaching their goals.</p> <p>Ryan is going to be faced with danger, intrigue, and a need to sacrifice for the greater good. But will it be enough?</p>"; 
